        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Recovery</td>
          <td>Single-flight half-open probe, exponential backoff with jitter, <code>Retry-After</code> honored as a floor</td>
          <td>Deployment returns when <code>cooldown_time</code> expires <a href="#references">[3]</a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Failover boundary</td>
          <td>In-flight, before the first byte, across protocol families</td>
          <td>Retry after the failed call returns <a href="#references">[3]</a></td>
        </tr>
